text: Jo Geon-haeng (born 7 February 1965) is a South Korean former cyclist. He competed in the team time trial event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of South Korea Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
